{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"<template>","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>El <strong>elemento</strong> <strong>HTML <code>&lt;template&gt;</code></strong> es un mecanismo para mantener el contenido <a href=\"/es/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> del lado del cliente que no se renderiza cuando se carga una página, pero que posteriormente puede ser instanciado durante el tiempo de ejecución empleando JavaScript.</p>\n<p>Piensa en la plantilla como un fragmento de contenido que está siendo almacenado para un uso posterior en el documento. El analizador procesa el contenido del elemento <strong><code>&lt;template&gt;</code></strong> durante la carga de la página, pero sólo lo hace para asegurar que esos contenidos son válidos; sin embargo, estos contenidos del elemento no se renderizan.</p>\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Categorías de Contenido (en-US)</a></th>\n      <th><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#metadata_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Metadata content (en-US)</a>, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#flow_content\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">flow content (en-US)</a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>, script-supporting element</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Contenido permitido</td>\n      <td>Sin restricciones</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Omisión de etiquetas</td>\n      <td>None, both the starting and ending tag are mandatory.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Padres permitidos</td>\n      <td>Cualquier elemento que acepte <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#metadata_content\">metadata content</a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#phrasing_content\">phrasing content</a>, o <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/Guide/HTML/Content_categories#script-supporting_elements\">script-supporting elements</a>. También se permiten como hijos de un elemento <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/colgroup\"><code>&lt;colgroup&gt;</code></a> que no tenga un atributo <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/colgroup#attr-span\"><code>span</code></a> .</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Implicit ARIA role</td>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html-aria/#dfn-no-corresponding-role\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">No corresponding role</a></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Permitted ARIA roles</td>\n      <td>No <code>role</code> permitted</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>DOM interface</td>\n      <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"atributos","title":"Atributos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Este elemento sólo incluye <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Global_attributes\">atributos globales</a>.</p>\n<p>SInembargo, <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> tiene una propiedad <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement/content\"><code>content</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>, que es solo-lectura cuyo <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a> contiene el subárbol DOM que representa a la plantilla.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplo","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Primero empezamos con la parte HTML del ejemplo.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>table</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>producttable<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>thead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>UPC_Code<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Product_Name<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>thead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tbody</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- datos opcionales pueden incluirse aquí opcionalmente --&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tbody</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>template</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>productrow<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>td</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>record<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>td</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>template</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Inicialmente tenemos una tabla en la cual insertaremos más tarde contenido usando código JavaScript. Más abajo viene el template, el cual describe la estructura de un fragmento HTML representando la fila de una tabla.</p>\n<p>Ahora que la tabla ha sido creada y el template definido, usamos JavaScript para insertar filas en la tabla, con cada fila siendo construida usando el template como su base.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Comprobar si el navegador soporta el elemento HTML template element chequeando</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// si tiene el atributo 'content'</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'content'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">createElement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'template'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Instanciar la tabla con el tbody existente</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// y la fila con el template</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> t <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#productrow'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  td <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> t<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"td\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  td<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"1235646565\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  td<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Stuff\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Clonar la nueva fila e insertarla en la tabla</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> tb <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"tbody\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> clone <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">importNode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>t<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  tb<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>clone<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Crear una nueva fila</span>\n  td<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"0384928528\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  td<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Acme Kidney Beans\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Clonar la nueva fila e insertarla en la tabla</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> clone2 <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">importNode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>t<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>content<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  tb<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">appendChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>clone2<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Buscar otra manera de añadir filas a la tabla porque el</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// elemento template no está soportado.</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>El resultado es la tabla HTML original HTML , con dos nuevas filas adjuntadas via JavaScript:</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css hidden notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">table</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #000<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">table td</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #fff<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Ejemplo\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"500\" height=\"120\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Especificación</th>\n      <th>Estado</th>\n      <th>Comentario</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/scripting.html#the-template-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'template element' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n      <td></td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52//scripting-1.html#the-template-element\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"es\">La definición de 'template element' en esta especificación.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n      <td>Initial definition</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidad navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"html.elements.template","dataURL":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_también","title":"Ver también","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>Web components: <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/slot\"><code>&lt;slot&gt;</code></a> (e históríco: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element/shadow\"><code>&lt;shadow&gt;</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>)</li>\n  <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/Web_Components/Using_templates_and_slots\">Usando templates y slots</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Atributos","id":"atributos"},{"text":"Ejemplo","id":"ejemplo"},{"text":"Especificaciones","id":"especificaciones"},{"text":"Compatibilidad navegadores","id":"compatibilidad_navegadores"},{"text":"Ver también","id":"ver_también"}],"summary":"El elemento HTML <template> es un mecanismo para mantener el contenido HTML del lado del cliente que no se renderiza cuando se carga una página, pero que posteriormente puede ser instanciado durante el tiempo de ejecución empleando JavaScript.","popularity":0.001,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<template>: The Content Template element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"<template>","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<template>: コンテンツテンプレート要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<template>: 콘텐츠 템플릿 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<template>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<template>: элемент шаблона контента","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"<template>：内容模板元素","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"<template>","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/html/element/template","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/html/element/template/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: Lenguaje de etiquetas de hipertexto"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Referencia de Elementos HTML"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/HTML/Element/template","title":"<template>"}],"pageTitle":"<template> - HTML: Lenguaje de etiquetas de hipertexto | MDN","noIndexing":false}}